title: [Signamtocs' Weaponry]
[Signamtocs' Magic Shoppe]
description: Beneath an uneven wooden ceiling, a tattered merchant permit hangs on one of the crumbling brick walls.  A plain wooden table sits in one corner while a worn rug rests on the sand floor.

A tattered merchant permit hangs on one of the crumbling brick walls, and an uneven wooden ceiling rises overhead.  A worn rug sits in one corner of a scattered sand floor.  There is an oversized sea chest on one side of the shop and a plain wooden table on the other.
